title: Airbnb Listings in Europe
text: Over the last several years Airbnb vacation rentals have been rising in popularity across all major European cities. Using Airbnb listing data compiled by researchers at the University of Warsaw, I seek to understand the factors contributing high guest satisfaction ratings and how those factors differ across European cities.
